ace in each compartment while maintaining a compact, stylish profile. The shelf arrives pre-assembled, requiring only simple wall mounting using the provided hardware — compatible with wall studs or appropriate wall anchors. With a weight capacity of up to 18 kg, it is sturdy enough to hold a variety of items securely. Ideal for living rooms, kitchens, or home offices, this wall-mounted display shelf adds a warm, rustic charm to any interior. Care is simple — just wipe clean with a dry or slightly damp cloth to maintain its natural beauty.\",\"language_tag\":\"en_IN\",\"marketplace_id\":\"A21TJRUUN4KGV\"}],\"shelf_bracket_shape\":[{\"value\":\"Square Grid\",\"language_tag\":\"en_IN\",\"marketplace_id\":\"A21TJRUUN4KGV\"}],\"is_assembly_required\":[{\"value\":true,\"marketplace_id\":\"A21TJRUUN4KGV\"}],\"assembly_instructions\":[{\"value\":\"Mount The Shelf On The Wall Using The Provided Hardware. Mark The Desired Position On The Wall, Drill Holes At The Marked Points, Insert Wall Plugs, And Secure The Shelf Using Screws. Ensure The Shelf Is Level Before Tightening Fully.\",\"language_tag\":\"en_IN\",\"marketplace_id\":\"A21TJRUUN4KGV\"}],\"item_depth_width_height\":[{\"depth\":{\"unit\":\"centimeters\",\"value\":9},\"width\":{\"unit\":\"centimeters\",\"value\":71},\"height\":{\"unit\":\"centimeters\",\"value\":71},\"marketplace_id\":\"A21TJRUUN4KGV\"}],\"item_package_dimensions\":[{\"width\":{\"unit\":\"centimeters\",\"value\":73},\"height\":{\"unit\":\"centimeters\",\"value\":73},\"length\":{\"unit\":\"centimeters\",\"value\":10},\"marketplace_id\":\"A21TJRUUN4KGV\"}],\"product_site_launch_date\":[{\"value\":\"2026-06-17T05:38:42.584Z\",\"marketplace_id\":\"A21TJRUUN4KGV\"}],\"recommended_browse_nodes\":[{\"value\":\"1380538031\",\"marketplace_id\":\"A21TJRUUN4KGV\"}],\"specific_uses_for_product\":[{\"value\":\"Mug Display\",\"language_tag\":\"en_IN\",\"marketplace_id\":\"A21TJRUUN4KGV\"},{\"value\":\"Decorative Items\",\"language_tag\":\"en_IN\",\"marketplace_id\"