{"context":"ProductsService","level":"debug","message":"[DYNAMIC-MAP] Mapping \"product_description\" = \"Transform any room into a stylish and organised space with this beautifully crafted wooden wall shelf. Measuring 31.5 inch in width, this compact yet functional shelf is perfect for displaying books, small potted plants, decorative figurines, and other cherished keepsakes. The natural wood finish paired with a woven jute panel along the front adds a warm, rustic charm that complements a wide range of interior styles, from bohemian to Scandinavian. Whether mounted above a bed, in a living room, or along a hallway, this shelf brings both practicality and aesthetic appeal to your walls. The sturdy construction ensures reliable support for your everyday display items, while the open-front design makes it easy to access and rearrange your collection. Multiple shelves can be mounted together to create a striking gallery-style wall arrangement. Easy to install and built to last, this wall shelf is an ideal addition to any home looking to maximise vertical space without compromising on style.\" → \"description\" (Text Editor)","timestamp":"2026-07-22T15:42:21.501Z"}
