{"context":"ProductsService","level":"debug","message":"[DYNAMIC-MAP] Mapping \"assembly_instructions\" = \"Mount The Shelf On The Wall Using The Provided Hardware. Mark The Desired Position On The Wall, Drill Holes At The Marked Points, Insert Wall Plugs, And Secure The Shelf Using Screws. Ensure The Shelf Is Level Before Tightening Fully. If you prefer not to mount the unit, simply attach the included protective silicone bumper caps (feet) to the bottom of the rack. This allows the organizer to stand securely on any flat surface, such as a desk, countertop, or shelf, while protecting your furniture from scratches.\" → \"custom_assembly_instructions\" (Text)","timestamp":"2026-07-22T15:43:20.170Z"}
