{"context":"ProductsService","level":"info","message":"[DYNAMIC-MAP] Final ERPNext payload for FB-087Q-G767: {\"item_code\":\"FB-087Q-G767\",\"sku\":\"FB-087Q-G767\",\"item_name\":\"Woodwolf Dark Green Ceramic Coffee 350 ml Microwave Safe Tea & Coffee Pack of 1 Ceramic Coffee Mug (350 ml)\",\"description\":\"Enjoy your favorite tea or coffee in this premium dark green ceramic mug. Designed with a glossy finish and comfortable handle, this mug is suitable for everyday use at home, office, cafes, and workspaces. The sturdy ceramic construction helps retain beverage temperature while providing a comfortable drinking experience. Its elegant solid-color design complements modern kitchens and dining spaces. Microwave-safe and easy to clean, this mug is ideal for coffee, tea, milk, hot chocolate, and other beverages. Key Benefits: Premium ceramic construction Elegant glossy dark green finish Comfortable ergonomic handle Microwave-safe design Suitable for home and office use Easy to clean and maintain Ideal for hot and cold beverages\",\"item_group\":\"Products\",\"custom_amazon\":1,\"disabled\":0,\"is_sales_item\":0,\"has_variants\":1,\"attributes\":[{\"attribute\":\"Color\"},{\"attribute\":\"Number_of_items\"}],\"image\":\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/31HOZVI57FL.jpg\",\"custom_thumbnail_image\":\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/31HOZVI57FL.jpg\",\"custom_amazon_product_type\":\"DRINKING_CUP\",\"brand\":\"Woodwolf\",\"custom_amazon_bullet_point\":[{\"doctype\":\"Amazon Bullet Point\",\"name\":\"child-mrwbrfx0-kpwcp\",\"__islocal\":1,\"bullet_point\":\"CERAMIC CONSTRUCTION: Crafted from high-quality ceramic material, this mug offers excellent heat retention to keep your beverages warm for longer.\"},{\"doctype\":\"Amazon Bullet Point\",\"name\":\"child-mrwbrfx0-yfwzw\",\"__islocal\":1,\"bullet_point\":\"RICH FOREST GREEN FINISH: Features a deep, glossy forest green glaze that adds a touch of elegance to your kitchen or dining table.\"},{\"doctype\":\"Amazon Bullet Point\",\"name\":\"child-mrwbrfx0-np9t7\",\"__islocal\":1,\"bullet_point\":\"COMFORTABLE HANDLE: Designed with a sturdy, ergonomic handle that provides a secure and comfortable grip while enjoying your hot beverages.\"},{\"doctype\":\"Amazon Bullet Point\",\"name\":\"child-mrwbrfx0-at0cf\",\"__islocal\":1,\"bullet_point\":\"VERSATILE USE: Perfect for serving coffee, tea, hot chocolate, or any other beverage, making it an ideal addition to your daily routine.\"},{\"doctype\":\"Amazon Bullet Point\",\"name\":\"child-mrwbrfx0-jvbs3\",\"__islocal\":1,\"bullet_point\":\"EASY TO CLEAN: The smooth glazed surface resists staining and is easy to clean, ensuring your mug stays looking fresh and vibrant with minimal effort.\"}],\"custom_item_type_name\":\"Ceramic Coffee Mug | Green Color | Single Piece\",\"custom_special_feature\":[{\"doctype\":\"Special feature Item\",\"name\":\"child-mrwbrgbz-unjma\",\"__islocal\":1,\"special_feature\":\"Cork Bottom Base\"},{\"doctype\":\"Special feature Item\",\"name\":\"child-mrwbrgj3-1afsj\",\"__islocal\":1,\"special_feature\":\"Easy-To-Grip\"},{\"doctype\":\"Special feature Item\",\"name\":\"child-mrwbrgq9-1qcui\",\"__islocal\":1,\"special_feature\":\"Dishwasher Safe\"},{\"doctype\":\"Special feature Item\",\"name\":\"child-mrwbrgy0-iid8j\",\"__islocal\":1,\"special_feature\":\"Glossy Dark Green Finish\"},{\"doctype\":\"Special feature Item\",\"name\":\"child-mrwbrh5r-am16k\",\"__islocal\":1,\"special_feature\":\"Premium Ceramic Material\"}],\"custom_select_material\":[{\"doctype\":\"Material Item\",\"name\":\"child-mrwbrhk6-o1fda\",\"__islocal\":1,\"material\":\"Ceramic\"}],\"custom_pattern\":\"Solid\",\"custom_size\":\"Standard\",\"custom_theme\":[{\"doctype\":\"Theme Item\",\"name\":\"child-mrwbrhze-sxe9h\",\"__islocal\":1,\"theme\":\"Contemporary\"},{\"doctype\":\"Theme Item\",\"name\":\"child-mrwbri6u-2qxpi\",\"__islocal\":1,\"theme\":\"Holiday\"},{\"doctype\":\"Theme Item\",\"name\":\"child-mrwbriec-b7fyf\",\"__islocal\":1,\"the